To install Vanishing Point to an Admin Section:
===============================================

1. Copy class.VanishingPoint.php, class.VP_Module.php, and all class.<plugin>.php to the includes folder

2. Copy conf.VanishingPoint.php to the includes folder

3. Below include_once("class.menu.php"); in class.controller.php put:
	require_once("includes/conf.VanishingPoint.php");

4. Copy and paste all code from class.controller.php's __universal_callback() function (between "begin VP code" and "end VP code") to the end of the __universal_callback() function.

5. Copy the jsPacker folder to the includes directory

6. Create a VP_Cache directory inside of scripts

7. In each controller, at the begining of the class add:

	var $vp_array = array(
		'default' => array(),
		'add' => array(),
		'edit' => array()
	);
And fill in the needed arrays.

Things to verify:

1. the HTTPPATH, HTTPPATH_CACHE, SERVERPATH, and SERVERPATH_CACHE are correct